You probably won't find anything for you to use. But you can try.

INSTALLATION
------------
Copy the file 'be.wellconsidered.backups' to ~/Library/LaunchAgents
Edit the file you copied and change the paths according to your current environment.

In Terminal:
------------	
	cd ~/Library/LaunchAgents
	
	launchctl load be.wellconsidered.backups
	
	launchctl list be.wellconsidered.backups # To verify the file is loaded.
	

More information:
-----------------
http://www.davidlanier.com/story/cron-and-launchctl-on-mac-os-x-105-leopard